<view class="page">
  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="title">AI 议程表</view>
    <view class="muted">首页用于领取首个管理员、进入管理中心和查看历史议程。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="status-row">
      <view class="status-label">云环境</view>
      <view class="status-value">{{envId}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="status-row">
      <view class="status-label">当前身份</view>
      <view class="status-value">{{identityText}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="status-row">
      <view class="status-label">OpenID</view>
      <view class="status-value">{{userOpenid || '登录中'}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel" wx:if="{{canClaimAdmin}}">
    <view class="title">领取管理员</view>
    <view class="muted">当前系统还没有管理员，点击后当前微信用户会成为首个管理员。</view>
    <button type="warn" bindtap="claimAdmin">领取管理员</button>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="title">管理中心</view>
    <view class="muted">{{adminTip}}</view>
    <view class="button-row">
      <button type="primary" bindtap="openAdmin">管理中心</button>
      <button bindtap="openHistory">历史议程</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section panel">
    <view class="title">解析议程表</view>
    <view class="muted">解析微信群接龙请进入底部“解析议程表”菜单。</view>
    <button type="primary" bindtap="openParseTab">去解析议程表</button>
  </view>
</view>
